[[Njiri]] (''warthog'' in English) imhuka yemusango iri mumhuri ye[[nguruve]]. Mhuka iyi inozivikanwa nezvinyanga zvipfupi zviviri zviri pamuromo payo. Njiri haisiyo yatinoti [[nguruve yemusango]]; iripo imwe humba yakafanana zvanyanya nenguruve dzinopfuyiwa pamba.

Njiri inodya [[huswa]]; michero; mwakwati emiti; ma[[zai]] nezvimwewo. Munguva yokunaya kwemvura njiri dzinodya zvisora zvipfupi zvirarama gore negore. Munguva yekutonhora mhuka idzi dzinodya midzi yemiti, nezvimabumbe zvinokura muvhu.

